A simple and responsive User Registration Form built using React.js.
designed to collect basic user information like first name, last name, email, and password.
This project demonstrates how to manage form data 
using React hooks, handle form submissions, and display a success message upon completion.

Technologies Used
React.js (Functional Components)

JavaScript (ES6+)

React Hooks – useState

HTML5 Form Validation

Inline CSS Styling

Future Enhancements
Add custom validation (email format, password strength)

Style with CSS framework (Bootstrap or Tailwind CSS)

Connect to backend API to store submitted data

♻Modularize inputs into reusable components

Display validation error messages









